Get data

e_get_data.Rd

Get data passed to e_charts.

e_get_data(e)

Arguments

e

An echarts4r object as returned by e_charts.

Value

A list of data.frames, one for each group.

Examples

echart <- cars %>%
  e_charts(speed) %>%
  e_scatter(dist) %>%
  e_lm(dist ~ speed)

echart
